data.text:
Value — Cap Hit (annual average salary) that the player has deserved to this point based on his stats, team performance and his contribution to team's result

Power Score — Cap Hit (annual average salary) that the player has deserved based on his stats, team performance and his contribution to team's result in the one season only

In our opinion, Value is more historically accurate than Power Score because it takes into account data from several seasons

Squad Value — total Value of all players on the team roster

Players Value — total Value of all players on the rosters of all teams in the league
